oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Tennessee Bicentennial Mall State Park map plaza
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Color photograph of two children sitting in the Tennessee Bicentennial Mall State Park map plaza. They are seated on a section of the map showing the cities Manchester and Tullahoma. Features a divided back, narrative, and a semi-transparent logo for the state park on reverse. [No. 327610]
